DevOps - It is about building culture, practices so as to deliver things faster. 
SRE - An implementation of DevOps. When we treat operation as a software it's a SRE.


What is toil ? - Work directly tied to running a service that is repetitive, manual etc

Toil based automation:
   - Automate manual tasks.
   - Automate interrupt driven or reactive tasks.


















